&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manama, Bahrain.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India achieved its best-ever performance at the 2025 Asian Youth Games held in Manama, Bahrain, winning a record 48 medals including 13 gold, 18 silver, and 17 bronze.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The 2025 Asian Youth Games were hosted by Manama, the capital of Bahrain.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s medal tally: 48 medals (13 Gold, 18 Silver, 17 Bronze) &amp;mdash; its best-ever result.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The girls&amp;rsquo; kabaddi team won India&amp;rsquo;s first gold, while Priteesmita Bhoi set a world youth record in weightlifting.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The event served as a qualifier for the 2026 Youth Olympics in Dakar, Senegal.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Asian Youth Games&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Organised by the Olympic Council of Asia (OCA).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Previous hosts: 2009 (Singapore), 2013 (Nanjing, China).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;2025 edition hosted in Manama, Bahrain.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s Highlights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;First medal: Khushi (bronze) in girls&amp;rsquo; kurash.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;First athletics medal: Ranjana Yadav (silver) in 5000m race walk.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Final day: 15 medals (7 golds &amp;ndash; 4 in boxing, 3 in beach wrestling).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Bahrain&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Capital: Manama.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Located in the Persian Gulf region of West Asia.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Hosted its first major continental multi-sport event in 2025.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Youth Olympics 2026&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Venue: Dakar, Senegal (West Africa).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s success in Manama served as a qualification milestone for the event.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;Swasth Nari Sashakt Parivar Abhiyaan&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Objective:&lt;/strong&gt; Strengthen healthcare services for women and children&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Launch Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 17th of this month&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Health Camps:&lt;/strong&gt; 75,000 camps at Ayushman Arogya Mandirs, CHCs, and other facilities&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complementary Measure:&lt;/strong&gt; Poshan Maah observed at all Anganwadis to promote nutrition and health awareness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Focuses on inclusive healthcare and empowered communities&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Encourages participation of private hospitals and healthcare stakeholders in the initiative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India won their 9th Asia Cup title after defeating Pakistan by 5 wickets in the 2025 Asia Cup Final at Dubai International Cricket Stadium.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s win in the Asia Cup 2025 makes it the team with the most Asia Cup titles, with 9 victories.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Man of the Match in the final was Tilak Verma, while Kuldeep Yadav was named the Most Valuable Player of the Tournament.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Abhishek Sharma was awarded the Player of the Tournament for his outstanding performance throughout the competition.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;India has now surpassed Sri Lanka (6 titles) and Pakistan (2 titles) in the number of Asia Cup titles won.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Asia Cup History&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Founded in 1984, the Asia Cup is governed by the Asian Cricket Council (ACC) and is played in alternating formats of ODI and T20I.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;India&amp;#39;s Record&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;With their 9th win, India holds the record for the most Asia Cup titles.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Top Performers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Abhishek Sharma scored the most runs and hit the most sixes in the tournament, while Kuldeep Yadav took the most wickets.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;BCCI&amp;#39;s Reward&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI) announced a ₹21 Crore prize for India&amp;rsquo;s victory in the 2025 Asia Cup.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

